# LConf Changelog

NOTE: Please read doc/upgrading.md for detailed information on changes and
upgrade information!

## 1.5.0 - XX/YY/2015

### CHANGES

* #424: Add icon_image and icon_image_alt to ldap schema
* #2680: Rewritten TreeBuilder export
* #2845: Icinga2: Use the default NotificationCommand 'mail-{host,service}-notification'
  if the contact does not provide {host,service}_notification_commands

### FEATURES

### FIXES

## 1.5.0 Beta2 - 10/02/2015

